  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Drink
    Drink CLASS This class is in the database DrinkDB and is an Entity that is stored in it The Entity will auto Generate a Primary key so that it is Unique to each Drink It will also store the title Description and price of the drink
    DrinkDB
    An abstract class which stores the framework of the database and the database itself This database stores the Drinks class as its entities
    DrinkListAdapter
    DrinksListAdapter is a class which uses Recycler View to display all of the drinks in the database
    DrinkListViewer
    A class used to display the DrinkList
